Comment.MultiLanguageText: Time horn is on for when request come through

AttributeList.Text: If Aux Pump running and not in Hand and no flush within in set time disable spin Aux Pump in Hand is Bypass for no flush interlock
If Aux Pump running and no lube, alarm
Fault if either TD pressure transducer signal is below 3.6mA
Reduce RPM if temp above RPM reduction temp Shudown if temp above shutdown. Reset either when 3 C below trigger point
If TD enabled and no charge, alarm
Set if any filter is plugged or charge above 1000

Turn on Horn if test or Sequence Pulse for horn time if any of following faults have a pulsed: FlushFault/Low Level/Tank Temp/LubeFault/FilterPlugged/Any Motor Start Fault/Charge Pressure fault, engine fault. Clock Horn for High Temp unless silenced Trigger horn 1 a minute if reduced RPM.
